<h3 id="hd_id3149107">Icon on the Insert toolbar:</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3148970" xml-lang="en-US"><variable id="syrahmentext"><ahelp hid=".uno:InsertFrameInteract">Draws a frame where you drag in the document. Click the arrow next to the icon to select the number of columns for the frame.</ahelp>
</variable></paragraph>
